single: {
  type: "install"
  message: <<EOM
CONFIGURATION NOTE:

To setup "redis" you need to edit the configuration file:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/redis.conf
%%PREFIX%%/etc/sentinel.conf

To start redis and sentinel as a service:
BSD
   add redis_enable="YES" in your /etc/rc.conf file.
   add sentinel_enable="YES" in your /etc/rc.conf file.

SunOS
   Use svcadm to enable ravenports/redis and ravenports/sentinel services.
EOM
}
